UMNUZ Mzwandile Masina uthi ulibangise emaphoyiseni wavulela imeya nosomlomo kamasipala waseKurhuleni, icala. Izolo, kusabalale ezinkundleni zokuxhumana ama-video aveza lo mholi weqembu eliphikisayo ebanjwe ngebhulukwe, ekhishwa emhlanganweni. UMasina usola imeya uNksz Tania Campbell nosomlomo kumasipala uMnuz Raymond Dlamini, ngalokhu okwenzekile. “Ngishaywe kabuhlungu futhi ngisashaqekile ukuthi ngiyilungu lomkhandlu elivoteliwe, ngigxavunwe ngaleya ndlela,” kusho uMasina. Kubemuncu esekhishwa onogada emhlanganweni woMkhandlu lowo owayeyiMeya yoMkhandlu waseKurhuleni uMzwandile Masina. pic.twitter.com/Tq8BhtqEGg Opposition leader Mzwandile Masina was removed from council.#BreakingNews #Ekurhuleni pic.twitter.com/o9BUZN8O91